Our Information Systems Division is currently developing applications using the 
Texas Instruments' IEF CASE Tool.  The development environment is OS/2 based, 
and the target environment is both Windows and VAX/VMS. Objects are stored 
locally on a server under OS/2, in DB2 Tables.  We are attempting to select a 
SCM Tool which will interface with both the IEF and SupportMagic for Windows (a 
help desk and asset management tool).  Has anyone successfully integrated the 
IEF with a CM Tool?  If so, we would greatly appreciate any feedback on how this
was done, which tool was selected, and an opinion on how well it is working.  We
would also appreciate any information on SupportMagic in an environment similar 
to ours.  Thanks in advance for any information you can provide.



